events.name: Texas A&M Aggies at South Carolina Gamecocks

headlines.description: Kenny Hill broke Johnny Manziel's single-game passing record with 511 yards, and No. 21 Texas A&M beat No. 9 South Carolina 52-28 on Thursday night, ending the Gamecocks' 18-game home win streak.
headlines.shortLinkText: A&M's Hill breaks Manziel mark in rout

events.name: Boise State Broncos at Ole Miss Rebels

headlines.description: Bo Wallace threw four touchdowns passes in a sloppy season opener, and No. 18 Mississippi pulled away in the fourth quarter to beat Boise State 35-13 on Thursday night.
headlines.shortLinkText: Wallace, Ole Miss pull away from Boise St.

events.name: Weber State Wildcats at Arizona State Sun Devils

headlines.description: D.J. Foster ran for 147 yards and three touchdowns, Jaelen Strong had 10 catches for 146 yards, and No. 19 Arizona State opened its season with a 45-14 rout of Weber State on Thursday night.
headlines.shortLinkText: Arizona St. erupts in romp over Weber St.
